- âœ… Automatic audit fields: `CreatedAt`, `CreatedBy`, `UpdatedAt`, `UpdatedBy`
- âœ… EF Core 9.0 optimized
- âœ… Supports custom user tracking via `ICurrentUserService`
- âœ… Minimal boilerplate (just inherit `AuditableEntity`)
